### Test a phi-4-mini-instruct workspace behind istio gateway
POST /v1/chat/completions
Host: localhost:5000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "max_tokens": 100,
  "model": "phi-4-mini-instruct",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a helpful assistant."
    },
    {
      "role": "user", 
      "content": "Tell me everything I need to know about the SCaLE conference."
    }
  ]
}

