### Ask a follow up question to the gemma-3-27b-instruct workspace behind istio gateway
POST /v1/chat/completions
Host: localhost:5000
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "max_tokens": 100,
  "model": "gemma-3-27b-instruct",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are a helpful assistant knowledgeable about the SCaLE conference."
    },
    {
      "role": "user", 
      "content": "Will there be any sessions on KAITO at the SCaLE conference?"
    }
  ]
}
